  "title": "(Entry Level) Customer Service Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Customer Service Specialist (Entry Level – Sales & Marketing Campaigns)</strong><br /><br />We’re looking for an entry-level Customer Service Specialist to support and execute marketing campaigns on-site. This role is ideal for fresh graduates or individuals who enjoy interacting with people and representing brands.</p><p><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>- Engage customers at marketing sites and events </p><p>- Provide basic product/service information </p><p>- Assist in sales operation for the campaign</p><p>- Deliver positive customer experiences </p><p>- Support on-ground marketing campaign execution </p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>- Entry-level candidates welcome (training provided) </p><p>- Comfortable with face-to-face customer interaction </p><p>- Good communication skills and positive attitude </p><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><p>- Hands on marketing exposure </p><p>- Training and career progression opportunities </p><p>- Supportive team environment</p>",
